input_bucket_id.description: S3 input bucket name (used for testing uploads).

mwaa_source_bucket.description: S3 bucket used by MWAA for DAGs/requirements.

mwaa_requirements_txt.description: Contents of requirements.txt to be used by MWAA.

mwaa_startup_script.description: Optional MWAA startup script content. Empty disables.

mwaa_webserver_access_mode.description: MWAA webserver access mode. Use PRIVATE_ONLY for best security.

project_name.description: Project/name prefix used for resource naming.

public_subnet_cidrs.description: Public subnet CIDRs (2 recommended) for NAT gateways.

s3_trigger_prefix.description: Optional S3 key prefix filter for triggering Lambda. Empty means no prefix filter.

s3_trigger_suffix.description: Optional S3 key suffix filter for triggering Lambda. Empty means no suffix filter.

tags.description: Additional tags to apply to all resources.
